<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وأُمُورٌ} عِدْوَة،<span class="c5"> بالكَسْر:</span> أَي بعِيدَةٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
